sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Browser)
    participant F as Frontend (Next.js)
    participant B as Backend (Express)
    participant W as EVM Wallet
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant E as Email/Telegram

    Note over U,E: === WALLET LOGIN FLOW ===

    U->>F: Click "Connect Wallet"
    F->>W: Open RainbowKit Modal
    W-->>F: Wallet Connected (address)
    F->>B: POST /auth/login/wallet/challenge {address}
    B->>DB: Store WalletChallenge (nonce, message)
    B-->>F: {message, nonce}
    F->>W: Request Signature (message)
    W-->>F: signature
    F->>B: POST /auth/login/wallet/verify {address, signature, message}
    B->>B: Verify signature (ethers.verifyMessage)
    B->>DB: Find/Create User + LoginSession
    B-->>F: {accessToken (15m), refreshToken (7d), user}
    F->>U: Redirect to Dashboard

    Note over U,E: === EMAIL REGISTRATION FLOW ===

    U->>F: Enter email + referral code
    F->>B: POST /auth/register/email/init {email}
    B->>DB: Create PendingSession + OtpCode
    B->>E: Send 6-digit OTP email
    B-->>F: {sessionId}
    U->>F: Enter OTP
    F->>B: POST /auth/verify-otp {sessionId, otp}
    B->>DB: Verify OTP (timing-safe, max 5 attempts)
    B-->>F: {verified: true}
    F->>W: Connect Wallet + Sign Message
    W-->>F: address + signature
    F->>B: POST /auth/register/email/complete {sessionId, sponsorCode, address, signature}
    B->>B: Verify signature + sponsor
    B->>DB: Create User (CONFIRMED) + auto-create SponsorCode
    B-->>F: {accessToken, refreshToken, user}

    Note over U,E: === TOKEN REFRESH ===

    F->>B: POST /auth/refresh {refreshToken}
    B->>DB: Verify LoginSession not revoked
    B-->>F: {new accessToken, new refreshToken}
